name: Susan G Taylor CRNA Corp - COVID Vaccine CLinic
notes: Join us for a free vaccine clinic on Saturday June 12th from Noon-2pm at Kulshan Brewing Company (K2- 1538 Kentucky Street)! Walk-ins are welcome for the Moderna first and second doses. As a part of the statewide Pints for Pokes initiative, Kulshan will be offering a beer on the house for any person who gets vaccinated on Saturday, and any person who has been vaccinated in the past month (May 15th through end of June). Folks getting vaccinated on Saturday will also be entered into the "Shot of a Lifetime” Million Dollar Washington State Lottery Drawing.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Rebel Med NW - COVID Vaccine Clinic
notes: ***We will accept both first and second dose appointments*** Insured, medicaid, medicare, and uninsured options all available. Walk-in's welcome, but will be advised to fill out information via this same sign up via kiosk. We are administering the first/second dose of the Moderna vaccine. Moderna is currently approved for all adults 18 years and older. Please bring a face covering that covers the mouth and nose. Everyone is required to stay 15-30 minutes under observation after receiving the vaccine. ****Rebel Med NW is located on the 2nd floor, with the entrance on NW Vernon Place above the nail salon. Across the street from the Olympic Athletic Club. ~~~We are an integrative medical clinic specializing in Naturopathic Primary Care, Acupuncture, and Mind Body Medicine.~~~ Please be respectful of the space as treatments may be ongoing. Please contact 206-297-6013, and ask to speak to a provider on call if you have a question, leave a voicemail and we will return as soon as we are available. Call 911 if life-threatening emergency, and you are in need of immediate help.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
notes:
Additional Information: ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!*** The
vaccination clinic will take place at Bale Breaker Brewing. This clinic will be
outside. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your
shoulder. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18
must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via
video/phone call or paper format.

Informacion Adicional: ***VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!!***
La clínica de vacunación se ubicara en Bale Breaker Brewing. Se requieren
máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. Todas las personas
mayores de 12 años son elegibles para vacunarse. Los menores de 18 años deben
estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los
padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
